{"tid":1283272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]強烈譴責反毛反共雙子林鄭月娥x盧偉聰","createTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:45:01.000Z","uid":27532,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff6206ee3430e628e29bebd55de9999732b12ed","tid":1283272,"uid":27532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"我地連登不嬲好尊重共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥同盧偉聰竟然同毛主席既精神背道而馳<br />\n果然是港英餘孽<br />\n<br />\n同時毛澤東在《湖南農民運動考察報告》中的一段話提到：「革命不是請客吃飯，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅緻，那樣從容不迫，文質彬彬，那樣溫良恭儉讓。革命是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動」，後來更被譜寫成毛主席語錄歌廣為傳唱。毛澤東實際上沒有慫恿人們崇尚暴力，但為暴力的施行提供了闡述，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 1966年8月22日，毛澤東更以批轉中共中央文件的方式，發出名為《嚴禁出動警察鎮壓革命學生運動》的明文規定：「不准以任何藉口出動警察干涉，鎮壓革命學生運動，警察一律不得進入學校」，從而為全國紅衛兵更大規模的打，砸，搶，抄，抓行徑提供了政治保護及政策保障。</span><br />\n<br />\nsource <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25AF%259B%25E6%25B3%25BD%25E4%25B8%259C&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0Oy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=3cbc1b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b740ecd03f8e6147801744ff75f2d05c858cf48","tid":1283272,"uid":27532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"374e3248587e122e136c29a29ef67697ec796047","tid":1283272,"uid":27532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"我唔洗解鎖手機"},{"pid":"3ba1c9a995bcbebf5408ebaa0304009a523df868","tid":1283272,"uid":27532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"我要見律師<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6c56be3f665221b7b09547df67b82bc06154b3","tid":1283272,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply